title: Telangana Bill to Divide Andhra Pradesh, THE ANDHRA PRADESH REOR
description:
This is the copy of THE ANDHRA PRADESH REORGANISATION BILL, 2013 introduced in Andhra Pradesh Assembly on 16th December 2013.

This is the copy as available on AP Assembly official website. However, it appears to be different from the bill "passed" by Union Cabinet.

If anyone could get the copy of the bill passed by Union Cabinet please upload it. If you can not upload here, you may upload at www.bayfiles.net and post the link in comments section here.

PLEASE SEED AFTER DOWNLOAD.

Post your views in the comments.
